
## 🆘 Troubleshooting

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| Bot won't start | Add DISCORD_TOKEN to Variables |
| No channels created | Bot needs Administrator permission |
| Buttons don't work | Must be in your own VC |
| "Missing env vars" | Add LOBBY_CHANNEL_ID |
## 🎯 Button Functions
| Button | Action |
|--------|--------|
| 🔒 Lock | Prevent new joins |
| 🔓 Unlock | Allow joins |
| 👻 Hide | Make channel invisible |
| 👀 Unhide | Make visible |
| 📊 Limit | Set user limit |
| ✏️ Rename | Change channel name |
| 🎵 Bitrate | Change audio quality |
| 👢 Kick | Select user → Kick |
| 🔄 Move | Select user → Move to lobby |
| 🚫 Ban | Select user → Ban |
| ✅ Permit | Select user → Allow |
| 📨 Invite | Mention user to invite |
| 👑 Claim | Take ownership |
| 🔄 Transfer | Give ownership |

## 🧪 Testing

1. Join lobby VC → Get private VC + locked text channel
